name: DHP_Elise_Metal_Dining_Chair,_Set_of_2
reviews: These chairs are perfect with our rustic/modern dining table. They are sturdy, comfortable and priced well.
Great look for us around the dining room with a farm rustic table

The chair seems sturdy but it is short. When pushed up to a table you can barely see it. When you sit in it, it is the right height but as I said it was supposed to be an awesome focal point for this farm table.
